Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.04,0:00:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,HUB. Multimodal CONUS movement planner for Marine logistics.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.05,0:00:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,LOGCOM problem set: contested logistics, supply chain, expeditionary\Nops.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.05,0:00:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Marine planners need one pane to compare road, rail, waterway, and air\Nto a POE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.06,0:00:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,BTS NTAD: 30 hubs, 47 typed multimodal edges, 10 USMC end-items.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick origin, POE, and end-item — Albany to Beaumont with an M1A1\NAbrams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A multi-step AI engine fuses per-mode capacity, clearance, and weight\Nlimits.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Three-click answer: recommended mode, named bottleneck, alternate\Ncorridors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Bottleneck named — I-10 Lake Charles bridge weight class — M1A1 NO-GO\Nwithout permit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Set KAMIWAZA_BASE_URL and the same code runs inside the wire —\Nair-gapped, IL5 ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.13,0:00:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Powered by the Kamiwaza Stack. Deploy in hours, not months.
